review_blob: Powerful and full-bodied lager, with a big hop profile. Long and rich aftertaste. Clearly one of the better lager

review_blob: Bottle (33cl) at Copenhagen Beerfestival  really black., allmost no foam, aromamix of coffee, roast malt and hops. So much power and it is really creamy. Pefect Imperial Stout

Get one of the first bottles, really nice sweet porter. Good harmoni with malt, alkohol and hops. Short dark creamy head.

review_blob: Just buy it and drink it now. Wow this beer got it all. Sweetness, bitterness, alkohol, fruit all in one. Perfect. Look forward to taste it to a great dessert.
really nice Christmas beer, The bitterness in this brew is doing it great to the Christmas food. Spicy and sweet aroma. Golden colour. Nice really nice.
Not many small breweries from Denmark is making a pilsner, but this one from Herslev is okay. God balance between malt and hops. Easy and refreshment.
Nice and special brew. Notes of vanila, chocolate, dried fruits. I think there are missing some rum notes and a little more bitterness.
This IPA have a okay balance. malt and bitterness is good, but there are missing something. A IPA the is okay but not special
I love this beer style, but this one i think is to easy to drink. I need some more power and taste. Golden colour,  some fruit and some bitterness.
More powerful than the hell, nice brew and good to all kind of food, refreshment and the harmoni is nice.
Okay beer, but nothing spectackular. Nice balance and easy to drink. Soft bitternes in the after taste.
Weissbier from germany is the best in the world, this one is really good but not as good as the ligth one. Good harmoni between malt, hops and yeast
Nice malty beer, really nice with good taste of caramel. Easy to drink, nice refreshment
This beer I have to drink 2 times to get the rigth impress. A good beer in harmoni, but strong so i need to get on it to taste it good. Nice
The best weissbeer i have tasted. Really nice and rice. The yeast, maltbody and hops do it really well. Perfect Weissbier
Really nice beer. Good body, notes of dried fruit. Sweetness and malty. A great beer to drink, when i need some ekstra.
